#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""Publish bounded RepoGround bundles for changed repository states only.

The publisher is fail-closed around generation identity:
- unchanged source + generator + configuration is skipped;
- successful publications retain only a bounded history;
- destructive storage cleanup is a separate, dry-run-by-default operation.
"""

